import styles from './index.scss'

import { TextMedium } from '../Text'
import Button from '../Button'
import Logo from '../Logo'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <header className={styles.wrapper}>
      <Logo />
      <Button>
        <TextMedium>
          Sign in
        </TextMedium>
      </Button>
    </header>
  )
}

export default Header
